    <description>.net 4, Can be compiled for different frameworks; See github project.

After adding package check servicemodel in app/web.config

Set your useragent and set add behaviorConfiguration to existing endpoints for WCF services which need a useragent

&amp;lt;endpoint behaviorConfiguration="AddUserAgent_Behaviour" &amp;/gt;

Based on:
http://msmvps.com/blogs/paulomorgado/archive/2007/04/27/wcf-building-an-http-user-agent-message-inspector.aspx</description>
